  "time_ut": 1661826905,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0ddd\u0da8\u0dcf\u0da7 \u0d85\u0dc0\u0dc1\u0dca\u200d\u0dba \u0dc3\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dc3\u0dd4 \u0db4\u0dc4\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0d9a\u0db8\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db4\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dcf \u0d85\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0db1\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The necessary facilities for Gota have been completed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna General Secretary, Member of Parliament Mr. Sagara Kariyawasam says that suitable facilities required for a former President have been arranged for Mr. Gotabhaya Rajapaksa.",
        "Accordingly, he said that Mr. Gotabaya Rajapaksa will visit Sri Lanka soon. At a press conference held yesterday (29th) at the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna headquarters, he said that he was there while answering questions from journalists.",
        "He said that Mr. Gotabaya Rajapaksa did not leave the country under a beautiful environment. Accordingly, Mr. Kariyawasam said that the necessary security and suitable facilities for a former President should be provided when he comes to Sri Lanka."
      ],
